# Exploratory Testing Notes

## Session Charter:
Evaluate usability and error handling across main user journey.

## Areas Explored:
- Registration & login flow
- Cart behavior
- Checkout validation
- Search functionality

## Observations:
- Inconsistent error messaging across forms
- Session remains active after logout in some cases
- Minor UI misalignment on product page

## Potential Risks:
- Checkout validation gaps may impact revenue
- Poor error handling may reduce user trust
